1
00:00:59,400 --> 00:01:04,400
兩千年前  戰國時期  中國共分為七個國家
{\an8}Two thousand years ago... during the Warring States period, China was divided into seven Kingdoms.

2
00:01:04,500 --> 00:01:09,500
多年來  七國之間為了爭權奪霸  戰亂連連  各國百姓苦不堪言
{\an8}For years they battled for supremacy while the people suffered.

3
00:01:09,600 --> 00:01:14,600
而在征伐諸國  試圖一統天下的七國君王中  秦王是最暴虐無情的一個
{\an8}The King of Qin was the most ruthless in his efforts to conquer the land and unify all under heaven.

4
00:01:14,700 --> 00:01:18,700
他被其他六國視為共同的威脅
{\an8}He was regarded as a common threat by the other six Kingdoms.

5
00:01:18,800 --> 00:01:23,800
中國歷代編年史中記載了許多刺殺君王的史實
{\an8}The annals of Chinese history are abound with tales of the assassins sent to kill the great King.

6
00:01:24,500 --> 00:01:29,000
這是其中的一個傳奇故事
{\an8}This is one of those legends...

7
00:02:13,670 --> 00:02:15,830
我  自幼便為孤兒
I was orphaned at an early age.

8
00:02:16,110 --> 00:02:18,700
也沒有名字  人稱無名
I had no name, so people called me Nameless.

9
00:02:19,450 --> 00:02:22,040
人若無名  便可專心練劍
Being a nobody, I studied swordsmanship.

10
00:02:22,550 --> 00:02:23,350
我花十年
After 10 years of practice,

11
00:02:23,520 --> 00:02:25,490
練成一種獨特劍法
I acquired a unique skill.

12
00:02:26,490 --> 00:02:28,320
秦王緊急召見我
The King of Qin has summoned me.

13
00:02:28,590 --> 00:02:32,120
是因為我已辦成一件驚動秦國的大事
My deeds have astonished the Kingdom.

14
00:03:10,710 --> 00:03:11,910
臣奉我王之命
By order of his Majesty,

15
00:03:12,080 --> 00:03:15,210
接壯士星夜兼程趕回  拜見丞相
we have brought the mighty warrior.

16
00:03:35,610 --> 00:03:38,840
長空  飛雪  殘劍
Sky, Flying Snow and Broken Sword,

17
00:03:39,780 --> 00:03:41,810
這三名趙國刺客
the three assassins from Zhao

18
00:03:42,020 --> 00:03:44,610
十年來謀刺我王
have sought his Majesty's life. For 10 years

19
00:03:44,820 --> 00:03:48,120
令我王一日不得安睡
his Majesty has known no peace.

20
00:03:49,800 --> 00:03:50,990
怎料今日
To the astonishment of all

21
00:03:51,160 --> 00:03:54,930
卻被我大秦壯士一舉擊破
a mighty warrior of Qin has smashed them.

22
00:03:55,370 --> 00:04:00,210
從此我王可以高枕無憂了
His Majesty can finally sleep at night!

23
00:04:00,440 --> 00:04:03,140
臣等恭賀我王
We rejoice for our King!

24
00:04:03,310 --> 00:04:04,940
天降壯士
This warrior sent from heaven

25
00:04:05,180 --> 00:04:07,150
剪除刺客
has exterminated the assassins.

26
00:04:25,710 --> 00:04:28,180
大王令  召壯士
Summon the warrior!

27
00:05:10,600 --> 00:05:13,660
上殿拜見大王  需在百步之外
Remain 100 paces from his Majesty.

28
00:05:13,910 --> 00:05:17,360
否則格殺勿論  壯士切記
Or you will be executed. Never forget that.

29
00:05:49,920 --> 00:05:53,980
十年來  從未有人上殿近寡人百步
No one is allowed within 100 paces of me.

30
00:05:54,190 --> 00:05:55,320
可知為何
Do you know why?

31
00:05:55,790 --> 00:05:57,190
刺客猖獗
To guard against assassins.

32
00:05:58,060 --> 00:06:01,970
不錯  刺客一日不除  我難解甲冑
Yes. That's why I am confined in this armor.

33
00:06:02,130 --> 00:06:05,100
如今你替寡人除此大害
You have removed a great peril for me.

34
00:06:05,770 --> 00:06:07,470
要何封賞
How should I reward you?

35
00:06:07,940 --> 00:06:10,240
為秦殺賊  不求封賞
My service was for Qin, not for a reward.

36
00:06:10,750 --> 00:06:13,510
大秦治下  必有封賞
Achievements must be rewarded.

37
00:06:19,160 --> 00:06:21,650
長空銀槍
Sky's silver spear...

38
00:06:23,260 --> 00:06:26,990
曾傷我大秦多少壯士
wounded many of my brave warriors.

39
00:06:28,670 --> 00:06:29,730
宣我法令
Announce my edict!

40
00:06:30,040 --> 00:06:31,130
大王法令
By order of his Majesty,

41
00:06:31,310 --> 00:06:35,640
有破刺客長空者  賞千金  封千戶侯
he who kills Sky will receive gold and land

42
00:06:35,810 --> 00:06:37,140
上殿二十步
and be allowed to drink

43
00:06:37,310 --> 00:06:38,780
與王對飲
within 20 paces of his Majesty.

44
00:06:59,440 --> 00:07:02,840
據寡人接報  你是我秦國人
I am informed you're a citizen of Qin.

45
00:07:03,080 --> 00:07:05,510
臣  狼孟縣亭長無名
I am a Prefect from Leng Meng County.

46
00:07:05,680 --> 00:07:08,710
區區亭長  轄區不過十里
A County Prefect over 10 square miles!

47
00:07:08,960 --> 00:07:12,080
是我大秦國最小的官吏
Surely the lowest-ranking official in Qin

48
00:07:12,490 --> 00:07:16,450
有何本事  能破趙國的三大刺客
how did you defeat such opponents?

49
00:07:16,930 --> 00:07:18,060
各個擊破
I took them on one by one.

50
00:07:19,100 --> 00:07:20,230
仔細講來
Tell me the details.

51
00:07:20,640 --> 00:07:21,760
大王可知
Does Your Majesty know

52
00:07:22,000 --> 00:07:24,300
殘劍  飛雪為一對情侶
Flying Snow and Broken Sword were lovers?

53
00:07:24,540 --> 00:07:26,010
寡人知道
Yes, I do.

54
00:07:26,280 --> 00:07:29,110
大王可曾聽說  他們三年無話
And that they hadn't spoken for three years?

55
00:07:29,480 --> 00:07:31,810
三年無話  為何
For three years? Why?

56
00:07:32,020 --> 00:07:34,950
皆因飛雪與長空曾有一夜之情
Flying Snow had an affair with Sky.

57
00:07:36,020 --> 00:07:37,750
使殘劍耿耿於懷
Broken Sword never forgave her.

58
00:07:38,130 --> 00:07:40,460
寡人怎麼未曾聽說呀
Why haven't I heard this before?

59
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:44,130
臣想方設法  才獲此秘情
I went to great lengths to uncover it.

60
00:07:45,800 --> 00:07:47,770
所以分化殘劍飛雪
To divide Flying Snow and Broken Sword.

61
00:07:48,140 --> 00:07:49,730
必先取長空
I first needed to eliminate Sky.

62
00:07:51,040 --> 00:07:54,010
你的做法  寡人猜到一二了
I have an idea of what you planned.

63
00:07:54,210 --> 00:07:55,680
大王賢明
Your Majesty is wise.

64
00:07:56,150 --> 00:07:58,310
對長空  你以何為戰
What did you use to defeat Sky?

65
00:07:59,620 --> 00:08:00,680
劍
The sword.

66
00:08:02,360 --> 00:08:05,820
在狼孟縣  臣掌管緝捕盜賊
I must arrest criminals in my county.

67
00:08:06,100 --> 00:08:07,120
六月初五
On the fifth day of the sixth month.

68
00:08:07,460 --> 00:08:09,860
長空在一家棋館內現身
Sky attended a chess house.

69
00:08:10,200 --> 00:08:11,330
臣打聽到
I had learnt he enjoyed playing chess

70
00:08:11,640 --> 00:08:14,370
他常來此地下棋聽琴
and listening to music there.

71
00:08:34,470 --> 00:08:36,590
秦宮七大高手
So, the seven masters of Qin Palace.

72
00:08:37,040 --> 00:08:39,330
跟你多日  拿你歸案
We are here to arrest you!

73
00:08:40,370 --> 00:08:43,240
亮出銀槍  驗明正身
Identify yourself by showing your spear.

74
00:10:35,320 --> 00:10:36,190
慢
Halt!

75
00:10:45,640 --> 00:10:47,830
小小亭長  有何貴幹
What can a minor official do?

76
00:10:48,540 --> 00:10:50,010
此地歸我轄管
This is my territory.

77
00:10:50,510 --> 00:10:51,480
如何
So?

78
00:10:51,740 --> 00:10:53,640
你乃大王通緝的要犯
You are on the King's most wanted list.

79
00:10:54,110 --> 00:10:55,410
我當拿你歸案
I am placing you under arrest.

80
00:12:31,840 --> 00:12:35,400
老先生  請再撫一曲
Old man, please play one more tune.

81
00:13:01,080 --> 00:13:02,810
武功琴韻雖不相同
Martial arts and music are different,

82
00:13:03,320 --> 00:13:04,750
但原理相通
but they share the same principle.

83
00:13:05,420 --> 00:13:08,010
都講求大音希聲之境界
Both stress attaining a supreme state.

84
00:13:09,560 --> 00:13:13,360
臣和長空面對面站著  有半個時辰
Sky and I faced each other for a long time.

85
00:13:14,100 --> 00:13:15,460
雖然誰也沒動
Neither of us moved.

86
00:13:16,370 --> 00:13:20,360
但決鬥已經在彼此的意念中繼續展開
We fought the battle in our minds.

87
00:16:09,720 --> 00:16:11,190
好快的劍
How swift thy sword!

88
00:16:14,330 --> 00:16:18,490
寡人自恃對秦國的一草一木瞭如指掌
I thought I knew everything about my Kingdom.

89
00:16:18,670 --> 00:16:20,360
卻不知狼孟縣內
I didn't know that Leng Meng County

90
00:16:20,610 --> 00:16:23,840
居然有你這樣的人才
held a talent like yours.

91
00:16:28,880 --> 00:16:29,970
殘劍
Broken Sword.

92
00:16:32,590 --> 00:16:33,820
飛雪
Flying Snow.

93
00:16:34,490 --> 00:16:35,460
大王法令
By order of his Majesty!

94
00:16:35,690 --> 00:16:38,320
刺客殘劍  刺客飛雪
Flying Snow and Broken Sword

95
00:16:38,530 --> 00:16:40,120
素來聯手行刺
have teamed up for assassination,

96
00:16:40,330 --> 00:16:42,860
有誅殺二人中任何一人者
he who kills either of them

97
00:16:43,070 --> 00:16:45,730
賞萬金  封五千戶侯
will receive gold and land

98
00:16:45,940 --> 00:16:47,030
上殿十步
and be allowed to drink

99
00:16:47,240 --> 00:16:48,870
與王對飲
within 10 paces of his Majesty.

100
00:17:09,100 --> 00:17:09,570
三年前
Three years ago, Flying Snow

101
00:17:09,800 --> 00:17:12,200
雙劍聯手攻入宮中
stormed the palace with Broken Sword.

102
00:17:12,370 --> 00:17:16,070
三千鐵甲竟不能擋
3000 elite troops couldn't stop them.

103
00:17:17,850 --> 00:17:21,280
從此寡人將這大殿清掃一空
I've since emptied the palace,

104
00:17:21,480 --> 00:17:23,980
使刺客無法藏身
so assassins cannot hide.

105
00:17:25,390 --> 00:17:27,550
你的劍竟能快過此二人
Was your sword swifter than theirs combined?

106
00:17:28,030 --> 00:17:28,750
不能
No.

107
00:17:32,230 --> 00:17:33,700
那你如何取勝
How did you do it, then?

108
00:17:45,580 --> 00:17:47,020
臣喬裝成趙人
Disguised as a citizen of Zhao.

109
00:17:47,280 --> 00:17:49,650
去趙國尋找殘劍飛雪
I sought them in the Kingdom of Zhao.

110
00:17:50,250 --> 00:17:51,410
臣探聽到
I learned they were hiding.

111
00:17:51,960 --> 00:17:54,220
兩人化名高山  流水
In a calligraphy school.

112
00:17:54,560 --> 00:17:57,320
藏身於趙國陘城一家書館
Under the names Highcliff and Springbrook.

113
00:17:57,800 --> 00:17:58,660
那天風聞
Rumor had it

114
00:17:58,830 --> 00:18:00,800
大王大軍將要攻趙
the Qin army would attack that day.

115
00:18:01,140 --> 00:18:03,370
陘城中百姓已逃散一空
Most of the townspeople had fled.

116
00:18:03,910 --> 00:18:05,570
只餘下書館弟子
Only the school's students remained.

117
00:18:07,080 --> 00:18:09,910
客人為何此時前來
Why have you come at such a time?

118
00:18:10,110 --> 00:18:11,140
你是何人
Who are you?

119
00:18:12,580 --> 00:18:14,350
在下趙國易縣人
I'm from Yi County in the Kingdom of Zhao.

120
00:18:15,150 --> 00:18:16,880
先父臨終留下遺願
My father's dying wish

121
00:18:17,360 --> 00:18:19,020
求貴館一副墨寶
was for one of your scrolls.

122
00:18:19,330 --> 00:18:22,660
今日  我書館已是最後一日了
I fear this may be our school's last day.

123
00:18:23,960 --> 00:18:26,730
客人求何人之字
Which calligrapher do you seek?

124
00:18:27,040 --> 00:18:28,660
求高山先生
I respectfully request Master Highcliff.

125
00:18:28,970 --> 00:18:31,300
高山先生  便是殘劍
Highcliff was Broken Sword

126
00:18:31,610 --> 00:18:33,130
傳說他由書法中悟出
Legend said his skill as a swordsman

127
00:18:33,340 --> 00:18:35,640
一套劍法  威力無比
was rooted in his calligraphy.

128
00:18:36,050 --> 00:18:37,840
臣對此頗有顧慮
So I had my concerns.

129
00:18:38,220 --> 00:18:41,380
所以臣想先看殘劍的書法
I needed to find out if it was true.

130
00:18:43,190 --> 00:18:44,280
求何字
What do you want written?

131
00:18:44,460 --> 00:18:45,650
劍
"Sword."

132
00:18:49,200 --> 00:18:50,720
客人是愛劍之人
You are fond of the sword?

133
00:18:52,800 --> 00:18:55,240
在下只是完成先父的遺願
It was my father's dying wish.

134
00:19:05,520 --> 00:19:06,650
幾尺
What size scroll?

135
00:19:07,820 --> 00:19:08,810
八尺
Eight feet.

136
00:19:10,690 --> 00:19:14,030
八尺劍字  需要硃砂
For that size I will need red ink.

137
00:19:14,530 --> 00:19:15,590
有客人求字
My master has asked me

138
00:19:16,630 --> 00:19:19,070
主人特向小姐借硃砂一用
to borrow some red ink.

139
00:19:23,280 --> 00:19:24,800
主人向小姐借硃砂
My master wants to borrow some red ink.

140
00:19:32,620 --> 00:19:34,350
不知小姐聽清了沒有
Did you hear me, Master Springbrook?

141
00:19:35,160 --> 00:19:37,250
主人向小姐借硃砂
Master Highcliff wants to borrow red ink.

142
00:19:40,600 --> 00:19:41,830
叫他自己過來
Tell him to come himself.

143
00:19:57,150 --> 00:19:58,480
弟子來借硃砂
Could I have some red ink?

144
00:20:47,290 --> 00:20:49,950
臣求的劍字  還沒有寫成
The character "sword" was still being written

145
00:20:50,360 --> 00:20:51,790
大王攻趙的軍隊
when Your Majesty's troops

146
00:20:52,020 --> 00:20:54,020
此時已到陘城城外了
arrived at the city gates.

147
00:22:15,900 --> 00:22:16,890
射
Draw!

148
00:22:19,800 --> 00:22:22,030
大王軍隊  之所以百戰百勝
Your Majesty's army is invincible,

149
00:22:22,210 --> 00:22:23,670
除能征善戰外
not only because it is brave,

150
00:22:23,880 --> 00:22:25,780
便在於弓強箭快
but also because of its archery

151
00:22:26,610 --> 00:22:29,880
六國的箭都不及秦箭射得遠
with a greater range than any other army.

152
00:22:30,550 --> 00:22:33,880
大王軍隊每到一處  必例行放箭
The Qin archers are like artillery

153
00:22:34,060 --> 00:22:36,530
試探敵情  威懾四方
intimidating the enemy.

154
00:22:48,880 --> 00:22:51,810
風  風  風
Hail! hail! hail!

155
00:23:35,740 --> 00:23:37,200
你們記住
Please remember

156
00:23:38,270 --> 00:23:40,260
秦國的箭再強
their arrows might destroy our town

157
00:23:41,010 --> 00:23:44,240
可以破我們的城  滅我們的國
and topple our Kingdom,

158
00:23:44,820 --> 00:23:47,150
可亡不了趙國的字
but they can never obliterate our culture.

159
00:23:48,720 --> 00:23:49,850
今日
Today,

160
00:23:50,160 --> 00:23:54,560
你們要學到趙國文字的精義
you will learn the essence of our culture.

161
00:24:21,900 --> 00:24:24,870
風  風  風
Hail! hail! hail!

162
00:24:44,890 --> 00:24:47,360
那些趙人  當真不動
Those Zhao people didn't flee?

163
00:24:47,600 --> 00:24:49,560
趙國書法  剛烈過人
They drew strength from their calligraphy.

164
00:24:49,800 --> 00:24:52,390
你所求劍字  有何難寫
What was so difficult about "sword"?

165
00:24:52,570 --> 00:24:55,230
劍的寫法  通常有一十九種
There are 19 different ways to write it.

166
00:24:55,470 --> 00:24:56,910
臣向殘劍所求
I asked Broken Sword

167
00:24:57,080 --> 00:25:00,010
是除去十九種變化的第二十種
for a 20th way.

168
00:25:00,280 --> 00:25:01,270
書法劍術
Both calligraphy and swordplay

169
00:25:01,520 --> 00:25:03,850
都靠手腕之力與胸中之氣
rely on one's strength and spirit.

170
00:25:04,080 --> 00:25:05,070
這第二十種
The 20th style would reveal

171
00:25:05,320 --> 00:25:08,350
便有他劍術的精妙藏於字中
the essence of his swordsmanship.

172
00:25:08,590 --> 00:25:11,560
一個字  竟有十九種寫法
How odd to write it in 19 ways.

173
00:25:11,930 --> 00:25:13,490
又互不相認
It makes the written language

174
00:25:14,000 --> 00:25:15,290
極為不便
impossible to comprehend.

175
00:25:16,600 --> 00:25:19,070
等寡人滅了六國之後
Once I've conquered the six Kingdoms

176
00:25:19,340 --> 00:25:20,740
再滅其它諸國
and all the northern tribes,

177
00:25:20,910 --> 00:25:23,470
必將這些雜七雜八的文字
I will eradicate this problem,

178
00:25:23,680 --> 00:25:24,800
統統廢掉
by mandating one style of writing.

179
00:25:25,010 --> 00:25:27,450
只留一種  豈不痛快
Wouldn't that be ideal?

180
00:25:28,720 --> 00:25:30,740
大王不是只滅六國嗎
Your Majesty won't stop at the six Kingdoms?

181
00:25:31,020 --> 00:25:32,750
六國算什麼
The six Kingdoms are nothing!

182
00:25:33,120 --> 00:25:35,650
寡人要率大秦的鐵騎
I will lead my army to conquer vast lands

183
00:25:35,990 --> 00:25:38,790
打下一個大大的疆土
and establish a great empire.

184
00:25:41,470 --> 00:25:44,370
風  風  風
Hail! hail! hail!

185
00:26:23,650 --> 00:26:25,280
是流水先生
Master Springbrook.

186
00:26:25,690 --> 00:26:26,880
為何離開
Why are you going outside?

187
00:26:27,330 --> 00:26:28,520
我去擋箭
To fend off the arrows.

188
00:26:28,860 --> 00:26:30,920
不用你去  退下
You aren't needed. Stay inside.

189
00:26:31,570 --> 00:26:34,430
秦軍箭陣  聞名天下
The Qin archers are powerful.

190
00:26:34,640 --> 00:26:36,600
流水先生未必能擋
You alone may not stop them.

191
00:27:09,010 --> 00:27:11,950
風  風  風
Hail! hail! hail!

192
00:29:06,270 --> 00:29:07,160
好身手
You are good.

193
00:29:08,130 --> 00:29:10,100
流水先生更是好身手
You are even better.

194
00:29:10,640 --> 00:29:12,040
你不為求字而來
You didn't come here for calligraphy.

195
00:29:13,940 --> 00:29:14,810
你是誰
Who are you?

196
00:29:15,340 --> 00:29:18,710
在下特地送一件東西請先生過目
I've travelled here to deliver an item.

197
00:29:21,220 --> 00:29:22,650
子夜藏書閣
Please meet me in the library at midnight.

198
00:29:31,300 --> 00:29:32,320
好字
Great calligraphy.

199
00:29:32,830 --> 00:29:33,820
好劍法
Great swordplay.

200
00:29:34,240 --> 00:29:36,360
先生並未看我出劍
You didn't even see my swordplay.

201
00:29:36,540 --> 00:29:39,300
若無你的劍  也無此字
I couldn't have written without it.

202
00:29:40,640 --> 00:29:41,700
今夜子時
At midnight

203
00:29:41,980 --> 00:29:45,070
請先生去藏書閣看一件東西
meet me in the library.

204
00:29:46,020 --> 00:29:47,450
大王幾十萬大軍
Several hundred thousand Qin troops

205
00:29:47,720 --> 00:29:51,210
當晚在山下安營紮寨準備攻趙
were readying for the next onslaught.

206
00:29:52,830 --> 00:29:54,730
臣則連夜悟字
I studied the character all night,

207
00:29:54,900 --> 00:29:57,730
想找出殘劍劍法之走勢
trying to unlock the secret of his skills.

208
00:30:09,380 --> 00:30:11,470
你說這字中有劍法
It would reveal his swordsmanship?

209
00:30:11,680 --> 00:30:15,420
可在寡人看來  這只是普通之字
But it's just an ordinary word.

210
00:30:16,860 --> 00:30:19,620
書法劍術  境界相通
Calligraphy and swordplay are similar

211
00:30:19,960 --> 00:30:21,660
奧妙全靠領悟
One must comprehend their true essence.

212
00:30:23,700 --> 00:30:24,860
你領悟到了
Did you discover it?

213
00:30:25,170 --> 00:30:26,430
尚未悟透
It eluded me.

214
00:30:26,770 --> 00:30:30,640
悟不透  你如何挑戰他們
So how did you challenge them?

215
00:30:31,080 --> 00:30:34,710
臣探之  殘劍與飛雪雖三年無話
Although they hadn't spoken in three years They spied on each other.

216
00:30:34,910 --> 00:30:36,400
但每晚子時
At midnight

217
00:30:36,550 --> 00:30:38,880
殘劍都會窺看飛雪
Broken Sword would peek into Flying Snow's room.

218
00:30:44,730 --> 00:30:46,130
而到了丑時
At 2 o'clock in the morning,

219
00:30:46,330 --> 00:30:49,560
飛雪同樣悄悄窺視殘劍
she would spy on Broken Sword.

220
00:30:55,710 --> 00:30:58,400
二人行為如此怪異
What strange behaviour.

221
00:30:58,710 --> 00:31:03,150
是  臣也驚訝二人關係如此奇怪
I was surprised too.

222
00:31:03,390 --> 00:31:07,120
特地送去銀槍  以求利用
So I used Sky's silver spear to get to them.

223
00:31:15,930 --> 00:31:18,130
長空是敗在你的劍下
Sky died by your sword?

224
00:31:18,400 --> 00:31:19,340
是
Yes.

225
00:31:21,880 --> 00:31:25,070
你是何人  為何來此
Who are you? Why are you here?

226
00:31:25,550 --> 00:31:26,950
在下實為秦人
I'm from the Kingdom of Qin.

227
00:31:27,150 --> 00:31:28,950
替長空帶來一句話
I have a message from Sky.

228
00:31:29,420 --> 00:31:30,320
講
Go on.

229
00:31:30,620 --> 00:31:31,480
長空說
he said he had lived a life

230
00:31:31,660 --> 00:31:34,520
他此生縱橫江湖  無牽無掛
without responsibilities or commitments,

231
00:31:34,760 --> 00:31:36,660
唯有一人常留心中
he cared for only one person.

232
00:31:37,930 --> 00:31:38,860
誰
Who?

233
00:31:39,230 --> 00:31:40,290
飛雪
Flying Snow.

234
00:31:51,610 --> 00:31:54,550
長空說  飛雪定會替他報仇
Sky was certain she'd avenge his death.

235
00:32:05,000 --> 00:32:09,300
若要同在下一戰  明日秦軍大營
To fight, meet me at the Qin camp.

236
00:34:30,450 --> 00:34:31,480
你走
You can leave now.

237
00:34:36,930 --> 00:34:38,190
走吧
Go!

238
00:35:13,810 --> 00:35:15,240
我知道你看見了
I know you saw us!

239
00:35:17,620 --> 00:35:18,810
我告訴你
Let me tell you,

240
00:35:18,980 --> 00:35:21,320
我跟她這樣已經三年了
we've been together for three years.

241
00:35:25,990 --> 00:35:27,930
我故意讓你看見的
I let you see us on purpose!

242
00:35:30,670 --> 00:35:32,600
我心裏根本沒有你
I no longer care about you at all!

243
00:37:18,810 --> 00:37:21,670
你我都很蠢
We were both very foolish.

244
00:37:59,460 --> 00:38:02,720
我只是要你對我好一點
I just wanted you to care about me.

245
00:38:39,340 --> 00:38:40,710
我不跟你動手
I'm not going to fight you.

246
00:38:42,020 --> 00:38:42,910
走
Go away!

247
00:38:48,060 --> 00:38:51,460
我要殺了你  為主人報仇
I will kill you in honor of my master!

248
00:40:20,840 --> 00:40:24,040
你既然找死  我成全你
You ask to die. I will help you.

249
