所以她氣血攻心  方寸大亂
she was disturbed and disoriented.

254
00:44:23,660 --> 00:44:25,520
臣嬴得絲毫不費力氣
I defeated her easily.

255
00:44:39,750 --> 00:44:41,610
想不到殘劍飛雪
I never imagined supreme warriors

256
00:44:41,780 --> 00:44:43,580
竟如此怪異
like Broken Sword and Flying Snow

257
00:44:43,750 --> 00:44:45,580
