是
True.

263
00:45:14,260 --> 00:45:16,950
你講的故事倒也合情合理
Your story sounds logical.

264
00:45:17,130 --> 00:45:18,220
可寡人看來
But,

265
00:45:18,430 --> 00:45:21,330
你把一個人想簡單了
you have underestimated one person.

266
00:45:22,770 --> 00:45:23,560
誰
Who?

267
00:45:24,570 --> 00:45:25,500
我
Me.

268
00:45:26,470 --> 00:45:29,870
你想不想知  寡人對他們印象如何
Would you like my impression of them?

269
00:45:30,680 --> 00:45:33,440
三年前  寡人曾與他們有過一戰
Three years ago they stormed the palace.

270
00:45:34,350 --> 00:45:35,710
在寡人看來
I was impressed

271
00:45:36,220 --> 00:45:38,310
這二人光明磊落氣度不凡
by their valor and dignity.

272
00:45:38,560 --> 00:45:40,320
絕非小人之輩
Their character could not be petty.

273
00:45:41,330 --> 00:45:43,590
所以  一夜之情是假
So Flying Snow's affair with Sky is a lie.

274
00:45:43,760 --> 00:45:45,390
反目成仇是假
Their betrayal of one another is a lie.

275
00:45:45,670 --> 00:45:48,570
你所講故事更是假
The story you just told is a lie!

276
00:45:51,870 --> 00:45:55,040
只有一件事是真
Except for one thing,

277
00:45:56,580 --> 00:45:59,980
長空認識你們其中一人
Sky did know one of you.

278
00:46:00,150 --> 00:46:01,170
誰
Who?

279
00:46:02,550 --> 00:46:03,680
你
You.

280
00:46:05,090 --> 00:46:07,750
寡人猜測  你與長空早就相識
I surmise you two were old friends.

281
00:46:09,430 --> 00:46:12,330
長空敗給你  只有一個理由
And Sky's defeat has only one explanation.

282
00:46:12,530 --> 00:46:13,520
什麼理由
What's that?

283
00:46:15,300 --> 00:46:17,030
故意求敗
He permitted it.

284
00:46:22,950 --> 00:46:25,940
你與長空為行刺寡人  暗自串通
To kill me, the two of you formed a pact,

285
00:46:26,150 --> 00:46:29,050
引我秦宮高手在一旁觀看作證
using my men as witnesses.

286
00:46:29,250 --> 00:46:31,310
布此圈套  並不困難
That was not hard to arrange.

287
00:46:31,520 --> 00:46:33,790
難在長空竟能將莫大信任
The hardest part was to persuade Sky

288
00:46:33,960 --> 00:46:35,290
托付給你
to put his life in your hands.

289
00:46:36,030 --> 00:46:39,290
你的劍雖快  未必能勝得了長空
You were not fast enough to defeat Sky,

290
00:46:39,500 --> 00:46:42,230
但長空卻自願倒在你的劍下
he died willingly under your sword.

291
00:46:42,600 --> 00:46:44,800
如此胸懷  令人嘆服
Such devotion deserves true respect.

292
00:46:45,170 --> 00:46:46,570
所以長空是你的
He was the first to sacrifice himself

293
00:46:46,740 --> 00:46:48,640
第一位捐助者
for your mission.

294
00:46:51,050 --> 00:46:53,540
寡人在想  長空心高氣傲
Sky was proud,

295
00:46:53,790 --> 00:46:55,450
自認天下無敵
he saw himself as an unrivalled fighter.

296
00:46:55,620 --> 00:46:58,350
他何以認定  他做不到的事情
What convinced him you could succeed

297
00:46:58,530 --> 00:46:59,990
唯你能成功
where he had failed?

298
00:47:01,660 --> 00:47:05,160
莫非你專為行刺  而十年練劍
You have trained, perhaps for 10 years

299
00:47:05,500 --> 00:47:07,600
你的劍術中藏有一式
with one goal, my assassination.

300
00:47:07,800 --> 00:47:10,400
威力巨大  無人能比
You have a great skill that few can counter.

301
00:47:21,020 --> 00:47:24,420
得到長空  你已能上殿二十步
Killing Sky got you within 20 paces of me.

302
00:47:24,590 --> 00:47:27,390
為何還尋找殘劍  飛雪
So why seek out Broken Sword and Flying Snow?

303
00:47:27,930 --> 00:47:30,830
寡人猜想  你所練行刺劍法
I surmise that your skill

304
