一定以十步為距
requires you to come within 10 paces.

305
00:47:33,870 --> 00:47:37,030
所以  你還需利用寡人的懸賞令
You needed a second sacrifice

306
00:47:37,210 --> 00:47:38,900
尋找第二名捐助者
to claim another reward

307
00:47:39,080 --> 00:47:40,640
再進十步
to bring you within 10 paces.

308
00:47:43,280 --> 00:47:45,050
寡人以為  殘劍飛雪
Although Broken Sword and Flying Snow

309
00:47:45,220 --> 00:47:47,120
雖與長空素昧平生
had never met Sky,

310
00:47:47,290 --> 00:47:48,380
但立即明白了
they instantly understood

311
00:47:48,590 --> 00:47:51,030
長空故意求敗的理由
the reason for his defeat.

312
00:48:04,340 --> 00:48:06,340
此處距書簡幾步
How far am I from the bookshelves?

313
00:48:07,980 --> 00:48:09,040
大約十步
About 10 paces.

314
00:48:09,450 --> 00:48:11,320
好  就是十步
10 paces is fine.

315
00:48:55,810 --> 00:48:57,680
在下只需一人相助
I need one of you to help me.

316
00:48:58,050 --> 00:48:59,510
兩位請自行決定
Please decide between yourselves.

317
00:48:59,920 --> 00:49:01,380
明晨  秦軍大營
Meet me at the Qin camp tomorrow morning.

318
00:49:15,370 --> 00:49:16,500
好快的劍
How swift thy sword!

319
00:49:18,270 --> 00:49:19,240
是
True.

320
00:49:19,710 --> 00:49:21,140
長空是當今大俠
Sky was a superior warrior,

321
00:49:22,250 --> 00:49:24,210
竟能將性命交與此人
he willingly gave his life to this man,

322
00:49:25,480 --> 00:49:27,280
所以他能夠刺秦
he can kill the King.

323
00:49:31,890 --> 00:49:32,980
我們要去
We must proceed.

324
00:49:33,890 --> 00:49:36,830
去  就是死
That means we will die.

325
00:49:39,700 --> 00:49:41,170
死就一起死
Then we die together.

326
00:51:00,710 --> 00:51:02,170
我比你晚了一步
You were one step ahead of me.

327
00:51:23,270 --> 00:51:25,070
我怕把你傷得太重了
Did I hurt you too much?

328
00:51:26,510 --> 00:51:27,800
應該是我去
I should be the one who fights him.

329
00:51:30,380 --> 00:51:31,810
我要你活下去
I want you to live.

330
00:51:32,520 --> 00:51:35,880
你死了  我怎麼活
If you died, how could I live?

331
00:51:37,890 --> 00:51:41,880
你答應我  要好好的活
You will live on, promise me.

332
00:51:50,040 --> 00:51:51,370
你說啊
Say it!

333
00:52:03,390 --> 00:52:04,450
好
All right.

334
00:52:13,900 --> 00:52:15,230
如月快要到了
Moon is on her way,

335
00:52:19,510 --> 00:52:20,740
我先走了
I had better go.

336
00:54:02,280 --> 00:54:04,270
在下狼孟縣亭長無名
I am Nameless, Prefect of Leng Meng County.

337
00:54:04,550 --> 00:54:08,070
捉拿趙國刺客到此  懇請單獨一戰
Please allow me to fight this assassin.

338
00:54:08,480 --> 00:54:10,250
此人是大王通緝的要犯
She is on his Majesty's most wanted list.

339
00:54:10,420 --> 00:54:13,290
既在此地現身  我當就地擒拿
Now she's here, I will arrest her.

340
00:54:13,560 --> 00:54:15,580
在下與刺客曾有言在先
The assassin and I have an agreement

341
00:54:15,890 --> 00:54:17,490
要單獨決一勝負
to fight one on one.

342
00:54:17,760 --> 00:54:18,730
如在下不能取勝
Should I be unable to defeat her,

343
00:54:18,900 --> 00:54:21,230
再有勞將軍援手相助
please apprehend her.

344
00:54:21,730 --> 00:54:23,100
望將軍恩准
Your permission is sought.

345
00:55:15,000 --> 00:55:16,690
出你的劍
Draw your sword!

346
00:55:47,980 --> 00:55:51,140
風  風  風
Hail! hail! hail!

347
00:55:52,350 --> 00:55:53,210
快動手
Make your move!

348
00:55:55,520 --> 00:55:57,990
風  風  風
Hail! hail! hail!

349
00:55:59,990 --> 00:56:01,620
為刺秦我死而無憾
I die willingly.

350
00:56:01,860 --> 00:56:03,120
請動手吧
Make your move.

351
