大風  大風  大風
Hail! hail! hail!

355
00:57:16,000 --> 00:57:17,600
好快的劍
How swift thy sword!

356
00:58:34,670 --> 00:58:37,840
你已拿了飛雪劍  為何還來
What are you here for?

357
00:58:38,780 --> 00:58:41,010
你曾說過一句話
For what you once said.

358
00:58:41,210 --> 00:58:45,450
是  誰傷飛雪  我必出劍
"I will fight the one who harms Flying Snow."

359
00:58:46,350 --> 00:58:48,350
請出劍
Please draw your sword.

360
00:59:00,600 --> 00:59:02,000
多謝
Thank you.

361
00:59:03,000 --> 00:59:07,140
寡人以為  你與殘劍之間也曾有一戰
I believe you and Broken Sword also fought,

362
00:59:07,240 --> 00:59:10,600
你們二人的交手絕非生死之戰
but rather it was.

363
00:59:10,700 --> 00:59:15,100
而是以此種方式祭奠飛雪
A fight to honor Flying Snow.

364
01:03:27,190 --> 01:03:28,310
主人交你此劍
My master wishes you to have his sword.

365
01:03:33,100 --> 01:03:34,300
為何交劍
Why?

366
01:03:34,640 --> 01:03:37,540
殘劍飛雪  生死相守
He and she are bound in life and death.

367
01:03:38,280 --> 01:03:41,950
人不離人  劍不離劍
They will never part, nor will their swords.

368
01:03:52,640 --> 01:03:53,900
主人給你此劍
It is his dying wish

369
01:03:54,340 --> 01:03:55,740
助你一同刺秦
that you take his sword for your mission.

370
01:04:32,590 --> 01:04:34,060
長空  飛雪  殘劍
Sky, Flying Snow and Broken Sword

371
01:04:34,220 --> 01:04:36,690
分別以不同方式捐出自己
sacrificed themselves,

372
01:04:36,930 --> 01:04:39,330
助你上殿十步來刺寡人
so you can be within 10 paces of me.

373
01:04:39,560 --> 01:04:42,050
此三人能把生命托付給你
All three gave you their lives.

374
01:04:42,270 --> 01:04:45,330
人生知己  也莫過於此了
The best of friends could not give more.

375
01:04:45,840 --> 01:04:47,270
所以  你才是
Therefore you are

376
01:04:47,440 --> 01:04:48,910
最危險的刺客
the most dangerous assassin of all.

377
01:05:02,290 --> 01:05:03,760
大王何以識破
How did you uncover my plan?

378
01:05:04,160 --> 01:05:06,030
寡人面前的燭火
The flames of these candles

379
01:05:07,600 --> 01:05:09,400
