01:05:21,350 --> 01:05:24,580
寡人自愧不如
I'm ashamed to say I am not that committed.

383
01:05:24,790 --> 01:05:26,780
大王畢竟識破了
Your Majesty has seen through our plan.

384
01:05:28,890 --> 01:05:31,290
寡人也是剛剛識破
If I had realised this sooner,

385
01:05:32,330 --> 01:05:36,130
否則怎會容你近我十步
I wouldn't have allowed you so close

386
01:05:38,370 --> 01:05:39,700
秦人不會刺我
A citizen of Qin would not do this.

387
01:05:39,870 --> 01:05:41,030
你到底是誰
Who are you?

388
01:05:41,240 --> 01:05:42,870
臣實為趙人
A man of Zhao.

389
01:05:44,510 --> 01:05:46,740
臣家人被秦軍所殺
Your Qin soldiers killed my family,

390
01:05:46,920 --> 01:05:48,320
自幼流落在秦
I wandered into Qin

391
01:05:48,490 --> 01:05:49,980
被秦人收養
and was adopted.

392
01:05:50,220 --> 01:05:51,850
十年前知道身世
I discovered my real identity 10 years ago

393
01:05:52,260 --> 01:05:54,160
便決心行刺
and set my heart on this plan.

394
01:05:54,760 --> 01:05:56,460
為趙而來
You've come to avenge Zhao.

395
01:05:59,430 --> 01:06:01,060
寡人明白了
I see.

396
01:06:02,300 --> 01:06:03,570
寡人想知道
I would like to know

397
01:06:04,170 --> 01:06:06,140
你練的快劍名稱
if your special skill has a name.

398
01:06:06,440 --> 01:06:07,770
如大王所猜
As Your Majesty guessed,

399
01:06:08,150 --> 01:06:09,610
藏有一式
there is only one crucial move.

400
01:06:09,880 --> 01:06:10,850
哪一式
What is that?

401
01:06:11,380 --> 01:06:12,850
十步一殺
"Death within 10 Paces."

402
01:06:13,220 --> 01:06:16,210
十步一殺  好名字
"Death within 10 Paces." A good name!

403
01:06:16,960 --> 01:06:18,050
寡人的衛士
All my guards are 100 paces away

404
01:06:18,260 --> 01:06:20,520
均在殿外的百步之遙
outside the palace.

405
01:06:20,690 --> 01:06:22,860
而你近寡人已十步
You are within 10 paces.

406
01:06:23,930 --> 01:06:24,920
看來
It would seem

407
01:06:25,570 --> 01:06:29,030
寡人今日是難逃此劫
that today I am doomed.

408
01:06:36,720 --> 01:06:38,380
你的殺氣在亂
But I sense your hesitation.

409
01:06:39,920 --> 01:06:41,440
大王見識過人
Your Majesty is perceptive.

410
01:06:42,290 --> 01:06:43,260
可是
However,

411
01:06:44,390 --> 01:06:46,660
大王也把一個人想簡單了
you too have underestimated someone.

412
01:06:47,860 --> 01:06:48,560
誰
Who?

413
01:06:48,760 --> 01:06:50,160
殘劍
Broken Sword.

414
01:06:57,610 --> 01:06:59,080
臣要向他們證明
I needed to prove to them

415
01:06:59,280 --> 01:07:02,610
臣的劍不僅快  且精準無誤
that my sword was fast and accurate.

416
01:07:48,840 --> 01:07:50,040
在下所練快劍
Within 10 paces,

417
01:07:50,380 --> 01:07:52,310
十步之內  絕無偏差
my sword strikes with surgical precision.

418
01:07:52,680 --> 01:07:54,950
若從膈腧穴入  步廊穴出
If it enters at precise pressure points,

419
01:07:55,150 --> 01:07:58,140
便能不傷臟器  令人傷而不死
it will not cause any fatal injury.

420
01:07:58,790 --> 01:08:00,550
只求兩位中任何一位
If one of you would take a blow

421
01:08:00,790 --> 01:08:04,320
能當眾受我一劍  騙過秦王耳目
before witnesses, we can fool the King.

422
01:08:06,670 --> 01:08:09,400
當眾受你一劍  豈是兒戲
Such a blow is hardly child's play.

423
01:08:10,000 --> 01:08:11,470
長空現在如何
How is Sky now?

424
01:08:11,910 --> 01:08:13,130
現已無妨
Fully recovered.

425
01:08:13,410 --> 01:08:15,740
難得他對你的劍法如此信任
His trust in your sword was extraordinary.

426
01:08:16,040 --> 01:08:18,270
秦王防範嚴密  無法接近
The King's security is impenetrable.

427
01:08:18,950 --> 01:08:20,210
只能如此
There was no other way.

428
01:08:20,650 --> 01:08:23,050
那些秦宮衛士  不值一提
His lmperial Guards were useless.

429
01:08:24,020 --> 01:08:26,990
其實三年前秦王就該死了
He should have died three years ago.

430
01:08:27,260 --> 01:08:28,230
何以失手
What went wrong?

431
01:08:31,200 --> 01:08:32,560
是我放棄了
I abandoned the plan.

432
01:08:38,040 --> 01:08:39,340
秦王不能殺
The King must not be killed.

433
01:08:39,810 --> 01:08:41,240
殘劍這樣講
He said that?

434
01:08:41,440 --> 01:08:42,000
是
Yes.

435
01:08:42,210 --> 01:08:43,200
為何
Why?

436
01:08:43,450 --> 01:08:44,810
臣也這樣問他
I also asked him.

437
01:08:45,150 --> 01:08:46,170
他如何作答
What did he say?

438
01:08:46,380 --> 01:08:48,410
當日殘劍不願細說
He would not explain that day.

439
01:08:50,590 --> 01:08:52,420
長空  飛雪  殘劍
Broken Sword is the strongest of the three,

440
01:08:52,830 --> 01:08:56,890
三人中唯有殘劍的劍法與臣不相上下
he and I are probably equal in skills.

441
01:08:57,700 --> 01:09:02,260
因此殘劍後來對臣說的話
What he told me later

442
01:09:03,040 --> 01:09:05,010
使臣頗有顧慮
greatly unsettled me.

443
01:09:06,340 --> 01:09:07,540
有我在
While I'm alive,

444
01:09:08,050 --> 01:09:09,640
便要阻止你刺秦
I'll stop you assassinating the King.

445
01:09:12,650 --> 01:09:13,950
我願助你
I will help you.

446
01:09:15,990 --> 01:09:18,860
三年前  有人錯失良機
He let the opportunity go by.

447
01:09:19,760 --> 01:09:22,200
這次  一定要成功
This time, we must succeed.

448
01:09:22,930 --> 01:09:24,760
明早  秦軍大營見
See you tomorrow at the Qin camp.

449
01:09:31,680 --> 01:09:32,970
你幫我一件事
Please do me a favor.

450
01:09:34,450 --> 01:09:35,910
出劍助我
Help me fight Broken Sword!

451
01:09:47,660 --> 01:09:48,490
主人
Master!

452
01:09:55,270 --> 01:09:56,170
還不出劍
What are you waiting for?

453
01:09:58,080 --> 01:10:00,240
臣雖答應飛雪出劍相助
Although I had agreed to help her

454
01:10:01,250 --> 01:10:03,340
但總以為有失正大光明
attack from behind is dishonorable,

455
01:10:03,580 --> 01:10:05,180
故遲遲不能出手
so I couldn't draw my sword.

456
01:10:06,150 --> 01:10:07,880
然而臣與飛雪都明白
But we both knew

457
01:10:08,190 --> 01:10:09,780
如不阻擋殘劍
if we did not stop Broken Sword,

458
01:10:10,760 --> 01:10:12,390
便絕無成功可能
we would never succeed.

459
01:12:04,170 --> 01:12:05,160
如月住手
Moon, don't!

460
01:12:06,780 --> 01:12:09,440
你不是他對手  住手吧
You're no match for him. Stop.

461
01:12:33,900 --> 01:12:35,260
我知道你會這樣做
I knew this would happen.

462
01:12:37,270 --> 01:12:39,000
這樣你就不能攔我了
You can't stop me now.

463
01:12:39,310 --> 01:12:42,070
就算傷我  我還會阻攔
Even wounded, I will still stop you.

464
01:12:44,050 --> 01:12:45,480
那我會殺了你
Then I will kill you!

465
01:12:53,480 --> 01:12:55,180
我怕把他傷得太重了
Did I hurt him too much?

466
01:12:55,850 --> 01:12:57,440
有小姐的創傷藥
Your special medicine

467
01:12:57,950 --> 01:13:00,440
一日後應無大礙
should heal his wounds in a day.

468
01:13:01,520 --> 01:13:02,620
藥送了嗎
have you delivered it?

469
01:13:03,230 --> 01:13:05,700
是我親手替先生敷上的
I tended to the wound myself.

470
01:13:06,470 --> 01:13:09,200
今天戰後  你捧飛雪劍
After the battle, take my sword

471
01:13:09,400 --> 01:13:10,870
跟來人進秦宮
and follow Nameless to see the King.

472
01:13:11,270 --> 01:13:12,240
是
Yes.

473
01:13:12,510 --> 01:13:14,740
秦國不會為難你這個下人
They won't treat a servant harshly.

474
01:13:16,040 --> 01:13:17,510
如刺秦成功
If the assassination succeeds,

475
01:13:18,410 --> 01:13:19,880
打紅旗回來
wave a red flag on your return.

476
01:13:20,520 --> 01:13:22,880
失敗了  黃旗
If it fails, a yellow one.

477
01:13:23,090 --> 01:13:25,350
小姐此戰若有不幸
If something happens to you,

478
01:13:25,560 --> 01:13:27,080
報信何用
any message will be useless.

479
01:13:30,300 --> 01:13:31,960
那我在天之靈
I will smile from heaven

480
01:13:32,330 --> 01:13:34,270
見紅旗也會含笑
if I see a red flag.

481
01:14:39,090 --> 01:14:40,110
飛雪如何
How is Flying Snow?

482
01:14:40,650 --> 01:14:41,710
正在養息
She is resting.

483
01:14:46,460 --> 01:14:47,860
我是背著她而來
She doesn't know I've come.

484
01:14:48,060 --> 01:14:50,860
你曾說過  有你在便會阻擋
You said you'd stop me.

485
01:14:51,470 --> 01:14:52,900
請你放棄刺秦
Please abandon the mission.

486
01:14:53,340 --> 01:14:54,600
你可知我是趙人
You know I am a man of Zhao.

487
01:14:54,970 --> 01:14:55,940
我也是
So am I.

488
01:14:56,370 --> 01:14:57,840
秦國是否要滅趙
Doesn't Qin want to conquer Zhao?

489
01:14:58,280 --> 01:14:59,240
是
Yes.

490
01:14:59,480 --> 01:15:01,310
秦王是否趙國的敵人
Isn't the King the enemy of Zhao?

491
01:15:01,750 --> 01:15:02,650
是
Yes.

492
01:15:03,450 --> 01:15:04,780
那你在替誰說話
Who are you trying to defend?

493
01:15:05,150 --> 01:15:06,480
你如何配做趙人
You call yourself a man of Zhao?

494
01:15:10,830 --> 01:15:14,690
你的話  飛雪也曾經這樣問我
Flying Snow has asked me that too.

495
01:15:17,780 --> 01:15:19,410
那年我浪跡江湖
When we first met,

496
01:15:21,120 --> 01:15:22,140
碰到飛雪
I was living a carefree life.

497
01:15:28,090 --> 01:15:30,890
那一戰  使我愛上飛雪
I fell in love with her after our first fight.

498
01:15:31,500 --> 01:15:34,060
飛雪是趙國大將趙震之女
She's the daughter of a Zhao general

499
01:15:34,500 --> 01:15:36,800
秦趙之戰中  趙震身亡
who died in battle against Qin.

500
01:15:37,200 --> 01:15:38,830
傳下飛雪劍給她
She inherited his sword.

501
01:15:39,840 --> 01:15:41,570
我知道飛雪立志刺秦
I knew she would avenge her father.

502
01:15:41,880 --> 01:15:44,540
為父報仇  便有心幫她
I promised to help her.

503
01:15:46,980 --> 01:15:48,950
書法劍術  同源同理
Calligraphy and swordplay

504
01:15:49,520 --> 01:15:51,550
我和飛雪每日習字
share the same principles.

505
01:15:51,960 --> 01:15:54,120
想從書法中悟出一套劍法
We did calligraphy to inspire our swordplay

506
01:15:54,430 --> 01:15:55,390
增進功力
and to heighten our powers.

507
01:15:56,900 --> 01:15:59,690
飛雪知道  我從小浪跡江湖
She knew I'd drifted since childhood,

508
01:15:59,930 --> 01:16:02,770
四海為家  便常對我說
calling no place home.

509
01:16:03,100 --> 01:16:04,300
等完成刺秦心願
Once we'd killed the King, she said

510
01:16:04,510 --> 01:16:07,530
就帶我回她的家  她說
she would take me to her home.

511
01:16:07,810 --> 01:16:10,570
那裏沒有劍  也沒有劍客
There'd be no more swordsmen,

512
01:16:11,110 --> 01:16:12,170
只有一個男人
only a man

513
01:16:12,420 --> 01:16:13,440
和一個女人
and a woman.

514
01:16:42,220 --> 01:16:44,320
書法之真諦  在於意境
The essence of calligraphy is from the soul.

515
01:16:44,590 --> 01:16:46,020
劍法也如此
Swordsmanship is the same.

516
01:16:46,760 --> 01:16:48,920
講求返樸歸真之境界
Both aspire to truth and simplicity.

517
01:16:49,430 --> 01:16:51,560
於是我慢慢領悟了
Gradually I recognised a greater cause.

518
01:16:59,180 --> 01:17:00,640
三年前  劍法練成
Three years ago we perfected our skills.

519
01:17:01,310 --> 01:17:02,940
飛雪執意要去刺秦
Flying Snow insisted on going ahead.

520
01:17:03,850 --> 01:17:05,910
我便隨飛雪一同殺入秦宮
Together, we stormed the palace.

521
01:21:44,050 --> 01:21:46,850
飛雪問我  為何不殺秦王
She asked why I had abandoned the mission.

522
01:21:47,280 --> 01:21:49,910
我告訴她  秦王不能殺
I told her the King must not be killed.

523
01:21:50,420 --> 01:21:53,290
這是我從書法的境界中悟出的道理
That is what calligraphy taught me.

524
01:21:54,730 --> 01:21:55,990
我沒有殺秦王
I didn't kill the King.

525
01:21:56,800 --> 01:21:58,490
飛雪從此不再理我
After that she refused to talk to me.

526
01:22:04,970 --> 01:22:06,270
請你放棄
Please abandon your plan.

527
01:22:06,780 --> 01:22:07,440
不
No.

528
01:22:07,650 --> 01:22:10,010
你的劍莫非只為仇恨而練
Was your sword forged in hatred?

529
01:22:10,250 --> 01:22:11,370
不錯
Yes.

530
01:22:12,480 --> 01:22:13,710
我的劍
For 10 years, it has never tired.

531
01:22:14,850 --> 01:22:17,450
十年來不敢有一刻倦怠
I can't stop now.

532
01:22:17,690 --> 01:22:19,250
你如何才肯聽
How can I dissuade you?

533
01:22:19,790 --> 01:22:21,090
除非你殺了我
Only by killing me.

534
01:22:21,860 --> 01:22:22,920
你一定要去
Are you that determined?

535
01:22:23,670 --> 01:22:24,630
是
Yes.

536
01:22:26,540 --> 01:22:27,730
那好
Allow me to convey my conviction

537
01:22:28,870 --> 01:22:30,700
我送你兩個字
in three words.

538
01:23:14,960 --> 01:23:16,360
字同我心
These words express my mind.

539
01:23:16,900 --> 01:23:18,800
望你三思
Please consider.

540
01:23:27,800 --> 01:23:30,900
如月  把劍交給無名大俠
Moon, give my sword to Master Nameless.

541
01:23:31,290 --> 01:23:33,190
我跟飛雪人不離人
Flying Snow and I will never part

542
01:23:33,290 --> 01:23:34,700
劍不離劍
nor will our swords.

543
01:23:49,580 --> 01:23:50,700
無名大俠
Master Nameless,

544
01:23:51,000 --> 01:23:53,000
如月雖身份卑微
although I am just a humble servant,

545
01:23:53,520 --> 01:23:55,520
也願為主人一勸
allow me to say a few words.

546
01:23:56,320 --> 01:23:59,420
如月身為丫環  八歲跟了主人
I've been with my master since I was eight,

547
01:23:59,890 --> 01:24:01,660
隨主人研習武藝
he taught me martial arts,

548
01:24:01,860 --> 01:24:03,860
更懂得做人的道理
and how to be a decent person.

549
01:24:04,800 --> 01:24:06,300
主人做的事
Whatever my master does

550
01:24:06,600 --> 01:24:07,800
一定不會錯
is for a good reason.

551
01:24:09,400 --> 01:24:10,900
主人給你寫的字
The words he has given you

552
01:24:11,100 --> 01:24:13,400
一定有道理
carry a deep meaning.

553
01:24:17,500 --> 01:24:21,350
如月只能為主人做最後一件事了
This will be the last thing I can do for my master.

554
01:24:22,500 --> 01:24:26,900
無名大俠  請你記住主人這兩個字
Master Nameless, please take his advice.

555
01:24:39,780 --> 01:24:41,000
為何如此
Why did you want to do that?

556
01:24:41,210 --> 01:24:43,010
我聽主人講過一個故事
I wanted to follow the example of my master,

557
01:24:43,250 --> 01:24:45,910
如月願效仿古人  以死相勸
and to persuade you with my life.

558
01:24:46,120 --> 01:24:48,550
你還小  生命可貴
You're still young. Life is precious.

559
01:24:48,790 --> 01:24:51,450
死  要死得其所
If you must die you should die for a greater cause.

560
01:24:56,330 --> 01:24:57,490
你去吧
Be on your way.

561
01:24:57,730 --> 01:25:00,260
該記住的  我會記住
I will remember what should be remembered.

562
01:25:17,420 --> 01:25:20,880
殘劍給你寫了哪兩個字
What were the words he wrote?

563
01:25:21,100 --> 01:25:22,560
天下
"All under heaven."

564
01:25:22,730 --> 01:25:24,600
天下
All under heaven...

565
01:25:24,800 --> 01:25:25,960
殘劍說
Broken Sword said,

566
01:25:26,300 --> 01:25:29,670
七國連年混戰  百姓受苦
"The people have suffered years of warfare.

567
01:25:29,970 --> 01:25:32,270
唯有大王才能停止戰亂
"Only the King of Qin can stop the chaos

568
01:25:32,610 --> 01:25:34,580
一統天下
"by uniting all under heaven."

569
01:25:36,180 --> 01:25:39,020
殘劍希望我  為了天下
He asked me to abandon the assassination

570
01:25:39,850 --> 01:25:41,510
放棄刺殺大王
for the greater good of all.

571
01:25:41,960 --> 01:25:44,580
他跟我說  一個人的痛苦
He said, one person's suffering is nothing

572
01:25:44,790 --> 01:25:48,090
與天下人比  便不再是痛苦
compared to the suffering of many.

573
01:25:49,170 --> 01:25:50,890
趙國與秦國的仇恨
The rivalry of Zhao and Qin is trivial

574
01:25:51,330 --> 01:25:54,830
放到天下  也不再是仇恨
compared to the greater cause.

575
01:25:59,410 --> 01:26:01,380
沒想到最瞭解寡人的
The person who really understands me

576
01:26:01,620 --> 01:26:04,180
竟是寡人通緝的刺客
is my most feared enemy.

577
01:26:09,790 --> 01:26:11,450
寡人孤獨一人
Alone, I have endured so much criticism.

578
01:26:11,660 --> 01:26:15,360
忍受多少責難  多少暗算
So many attempts on my life.

579
01:26:15,570 --> 01:26:18,000
無人能懂寡人之心
No one understands my intentions.

580
01:26:18,170 --> 01:26:20,570
就連秦國的滿朝文武
Even my court officials

581
01:26:20,840 --> 01:26:24,280
也視寡人為暴君
see me as a tyrant.

582
01:26:26,910 --> 01:26:29,880
想不到殘劍
But I never imagined

583
01:26:30,050 --> 01:26:32,180
與寡人素昧平生
that Broken Sword, my arch-enemy

584
01:26:32,420 --> 01:26:34,890
才真正懂得寡人
would truly understand,

585
01:26:36,290 --> 01:26:39,260
與寡人心意相通
and appreciate my real motives.

586
01:26:51,050 --> 01:26:52,540
寡人想知道
I would like to know,

587
01:26:53,060 --> 01:26:56,320
你手無寸鐵  如何刺我
how you mean to kill me without your sword?

588
01:26:56,960 --> 01:26:58,090
奪劍
By capturing yours!

589
01:27:11,980 --> 01:27:13,950
此劍隨寡人征戰南北
This sword has protected me

590
01:27:14,150 --> 01:27:15,580
也有十年了
through all my battles.

591
01:27:16,420 --> 01:27:19,580
寡人能有殘劍大俠這樣的知己
Having found a true confidant in Broken Sword,

592
01:27:19,790 --> 01:27:22,620
便是死  也足矣
if I die, I am content with my life.

593
01:27:24,430 --> 01:27:26,020
你就為天下
Let "All under heaven"

594
01:27:27,530 --> 01:27:29,560
決定這一劍吧
guide your decision.

595
01:29:35,400 --> 01:29:36,900
寡人悟到了
It's just dawned on me!

596
01:29:37,450 --> 01:29:38,650
殘劍的這幅字
This scroll of Broken Sword's

597
01:29:38,750 --> 01:29:40,900
根本就不含劍法招式
isn't about sword technique,

598
01:29:41,000 --> 01:29:43,600
寫的是劍法的最高境界
but about swordsmanship's ultimate ideal.

599
01:29:43,940 --> 01:29:47,100
劍法  其第一層境界
Swordsmanship's first achievement

600
01:29:47,200 --> 01:29:48,700
講求人劍合一
is the unity of man and sword.

601
01:29:48,800 --> 01:29:50,900
劍就是人  人就是劍
Once this unity is attained

602
01:29:51,000 --> 01:29:53,500
手中寸草  也是利器
even a blade of grass can be a weapon.

603
01:29:53,900 --> 01:29:55,090
其第二層境界
The second achievement is when

604
01:29:55,260 --> 01:29:59,200
講求手中無劍  劍在心中
the sword exists in one's heart

605
01:29:59,300 --> 01:30:01,900
雖赤手空拳  卻能以劍氣
when absent from one's hand One can strike an enemy at 100 paces,

606
01:30:01,970 --> 01:30:04,300
殺敵於百步之外
even with bare hands.

607
01:30:04,900 --> 01:30:07,000
而劍法的最高境界
Swordsmanship's ultimate achievement

608
01:30:07,310 --> 01:30:11,410
則是手中無劍  心中也無劍
is the absence of the sword in both hand and heart.

609
01:30:11,610 --> 01:30:12,880
是以大胸懷
The swordsman is at peace

610
01:30:12,980 --> 01:30:14,360
包容一切
with the rest of the world,

611
01:30:15,850 --> 01:30:17,650
那便是不殺
he vows not to kill

612
01:30:18,160 --> 01:30:20,000
便是和平
and to bring peace to mankind.

613
01:30:46,540 --> 01:30:50,730
大王  這一劍臣必須刺
Your Majesty, your visions have convinced me

614
01:30:53,910 --> 01:30:55,240
刺了這一劍
that you are committed to the highest ideal

615
01:30:56,220 --> 01:30:57,680
很多人都會死
of ultimate swordsmanship.

616
01:30:59,590 --> 01:31:01,210
而大王會活著
Therefore I cannot kill you.

617
01:31:04,260 --> 01:31:07,190
死去的人  請大王記住
Remember those who gave their lives

618
01:31:08,430 --> 01:31:10,360
那最高的境界
for the highest ideal: peace.

619
01:33:49,050 --> 01:33:50,720
無名已近秦王十步
No more killing Nameless went within 10 paces of the King,

620
01:33:51,990 --> 01:33:54,120
他的劍是不會失手的
he could not have missed.

621
01:33:55,600 --> 01:33:57,790
所以  只有一個解釋
There is only one explanation,

622
01:33:58,170 --> 01:33:59,790
是他自己願意放棄
he must have abandoned the mission.

623
01:34:01,440 --> 01:34:03,340
你到底跟他說了什麼
What did you say to him?

624
01:34:03,940 --> 01:34:05,340
我只寫了兩個字
I wrote three words.

625
01:34:06,140 --> 01:34:07,130
哪兩個字
What words?

626
01:34:08,180 --> 01:34:09,410
天下
"All under heaven."

627
01:34:12,550 --> 01:34:14,080
你心裏只有天下
That is all you care about!

628
01:34:14,320 --> 01:34:15,180
還有你
And you.

629
01:34:17,430 --> 01:34:18,360
我不信
I don't believe you.

630
01:34:18,630 --> 01:34:19,890
如何讓你信
How can I convince you?

631
01:34:28,610 --> 01:34:29,570
拔劍
Draw your sword.

632
01:34:32,240 --> 01:34:33,340
你害了無名
You've misled Nameless.

633
01:34:33,880 --> 01:34:36,370
害了長空  害了趙國
You've ruined Sky and the Kingdom of Zhao.

634
01:34:36,820 --> 01:34:37,780
拔劍
Draw!

635
01:34:41,720 --> 01:34:43,550
當初我們相識的時候
When we first met...

636
01:34:45,560 --> 01:34:46,960
你也要我拔劍
I had to prove myself to convince you.

637
01:34:50,300 --> 01:34:51,630
你如何才信
What can I do this time?

638
01:34:52,070 --> 01:34:53,660
我只要你拔劍
Just draw your sword!

639
01:36:20,790 --> 01:36:22,310
你為什麼不擋我的劍
Why didn't you fend off my sword?

640
01:36:23,790 --> 01:36:25,260
這樣你就信了
So that you'd believe me.

641
01:36:33,440 --> 01:36:35,460
我一直都想跟你回家
I always wanted to go home with you.

642
01:36:41,080 --> 01:36:42,550
可惜不能去了
Sadly, it won't happen now.

643
01:36:47,750 --> 01:36:49,240
你一個人好好保重
Take good care of yourself.

644
01:37:03,410 --> 01:37:04,970
你為什麼不擋我的劍
Why didn't you defend yourself?

645
01:37:14,120 --> 01:37:15,550
為什麼不擋
Why didn't you defend yourself?

646
01:37:26,840 --> 01:37:28,270
為什麼不擋
Why didn't you?

647
01:38:40,250 --> 01:38:42,540
我們再不會浪跡江湖了
No more drifting, no more roaming.

648
01:38:49,130 --> 01:38:51,090
我現在就帶你回家
I'm taking you home now.

649
01:38:53,800 --> 01:38:55,200
回我們的家
Our home.

650
01:40:10,180 --> 01:40:11,740
大王  殺不殺
Your Majesty, permission to execute?

651
01:40:11,950 --> 01:40:15,010
大王  殺不殺  殺不殺
Permission to execute?

652
