大王  殺不殺
Your Majesty, permission to execute?

653
01:40:17,820 --> 01:40:20,920
大王  殺不殺  殺不殺
Permission to execute?

654
01:40:40,790 --> 01:40:43,780
居心叵測  大膽行刺
He conspired to assassinate Your Majesty.

655
01:40:43,990 --> 01:40:45,320
殺無赦
Show no mercy!

656
01:40:45,490 --> 01:40:49,060
這是大王制定的秦國大法
This is the law of Qin!

657
01:40:52,040 --> 01:40:53,800
大王要得天下
To conquer all under heaven,

658
01:40:54,000 --> 01:40:56,060
一定要令行禁止
the law must be enforced.

659
01:40:56,310 --> 01:40:58,870
給世人一個榜樣
Set an example for the world!

660
01:41:00,880 --> 01:41:03,440
大王  殺  大王  殺
Execute him! Execute him!

661
01:41:03,650 --> 01:41:05,050
大王  殺
Execute him!

662
